{"tid":833722,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"高質天婦羅","createTime":"2018-09-23T16:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T18:50:50.000Z","uid":175988,"like":2,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8878dddd2f3398a6e6ad46f96951c3aea9694e45","tid":833722,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T16:48:19.000Z","msg":"<strong>天海 @ 上環</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Q9cG2kN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQ9cG2kN.jpg&h=8e770d93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>海鮮天丼<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n海鮮質素幾高，特別係蠔同海蝦，蝦身爽彈厚肉，蠔肉軟滑多汁，海水䶢鮮味濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n米飯粒粒分明飽滿且帶濕潤，入口煙韌有飯香<br />\n<br />\n天婦羅即叫即炸，皮薄脆口，微甜醬汁可以中和膩感<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n脆漿coating成日剝落，未能緊緻包裹內餡，好似天婦羅流心蛋咁，部份外皮完全唔見咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>結論: 午巿套餐要$180，抵唔抵食見仁見智，但我可以肯定呢間係我香港食過最好食嘅天婦羅之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong>"},{"pid":"9d48feafcec4c502297087495a2c6f594e895c1d","tid":833722,"uid":72054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T16:49:21.000Z","msg":"真心想問點個隻汁係叫咩名<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc75646c9dd725717a7a8c6293314f544e097f2f","tid":833722,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9d48feafcec4c502297087495a2c6f594e895c1d","tid":833722,"uid":72054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T16:49:21.000Z","msg":"真心想問點個隻汁係叫咩名<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T16:55:20.000Z","msg":"唔係就咁叫天丼汁/天婦羅汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582d26659176e566922bea913a7d77c262b7aa81","tid":833722,"uid":31076,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T16:55:43.000Z","msg":"依篇稿幾錢？"},{"pid":"30c2618cae653fb62ae861d9338a019138444dc9","tid":833722,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"582d26659176e566922bea913a7d77c262b7aa81","tid":833722,"uid":31076,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T16:55:43.000Z","msg":"依篇稿幾錢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T16:58:35.000Z","msg":"中立食評<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53567665228c4f211010a55d7a8c11a5b1d1dd1e","tid":833722,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T02:06:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20285144f476cd54c5c302c074dfcf0df5520ede","tid":833722,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:39:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5adac2599fca9cf6918f802f3adf38626f16385e","tid":833722,"uid":83648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T10:42:56.000Z","msg":"180蚊<br />\n痴線"},{"pid":"0b081f41bbbe9bff78f07b53d51c05350e6af13d","tid":833722,"uid":175988,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5adac2599fca9cf6918f802f3adf38626f16385e","tid":833722,"uid":83648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T10:42:56.000Z","msg":"180蚊<br />\n痴線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T11:36:25.000Z","msg":"海鰻+蠔+白身魚+海蝦+魷魚+帆立貝<br />\n<br />\n我覺得中環嚟講$180算係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0b8a5f67ced65d63e9499d8f276a5c3aff0a20","tid":833722,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T12:03:25.000Z","msg":"同天扶良比，邊間正啲"},{"pid":"42a9